discovery_rule.name: Fans
discovery_rule.description: Find basic system traps to search into about fans

trigger_prototype.expression: ({Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},Reading].last()} < {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},LowerThresholdCritical].last()})
trigger_prototype.name: Fan {#FILENAME} Speed is not ideal

trigger_prototype.expression: ({Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},Status.Health,{#COOLEDBY}].iregexp(OK)}=0) and ({Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},Status.Health,{#COOLEDBY}].iregexp(null)}=0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},Status.Health,{#COOLEDBY}].iregexp(no batch file yet)}=0)
trigger_prototype.name: Fan {#FILENAME} Status

discovery_rule.name: iDRAC
discovery_rule.description: Find basic system traps to search into about iDRAC

trigger_prototype.expression: {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},FirmwareVersion,{#MANAGEDBY}].diff(0)}>0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},FirmwareVersion,{#MANAGEDBY}].iregexp(null)}=0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},FirmwareVersion,{#MANAGEDBY}].iregexp(no batch file yet)}=0
trigger_prototype.name: iDRAC {#FILENAME} Firmware Changed

trigger_prototype.expression: {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},Status.Health,{#MANAGEDBY}].iregexp(OK)}=0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},Status.Health,{#MANAGEDBY}].iregexp(nul)}=0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},Status.Health,{#MANAGEDBY}].iregexp(no batch file yet)}=0
trigger_prototype.name: iDRAC {#FILENAME} Health Status

discovery_rule.name: PowerSource
discovery_rule.description: Find basic system traps to search into about power source

trigger_prototype.expression: {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},FirmwareVersion,{#POWEREDBY}].diff(0)}>0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},FirmwareVersion,{#POWEREDBY}].iregexp(null)}=0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},FirmwareVersion,{#POWEREDBY}].iregexp(no batch file yet)}=0
trigger_prototype.name: PowerSource {#FILENAME} Firmware have changed

trigger_prototype.expression: {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},Status.Health,{#POWEREDBY}].iregexp(OK)}=0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},Status.Health,{#POWEREDBY}].iregexp(null)}=0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},Status.Health,{#POWEREDBY}].iregexp(no batch file yet)}=0
trigger_prototype.name: PowerSource {#FILENAME} is not Healthy

discovery_rule.name: Processors
discovery_rule.description: Find basic system traps to search into about Processors

trigger_prototype.expression: {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},Status.Health,{#PROCESSORS}].iregexp(OK)}=0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},Status.Health,{#PROCESSORS}].iregexp(null)}=0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},Status.Health,{#PROCESSORS}].iregexp(no batch file yet)}=0
trigger_prototype.name: Processor {#FILENAME} is not Healthy

discovery_rule.name: SimpleStorage
discovery_rule.description: Find basic system traps to search into about storage

trigger_prototype.expression: {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-disk-reader[{#FILENAME},Status.Health,{#SIMPLESTORAGE}].regexp(OK)}=0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-disk-reader[{#FILENAME},Status.Health,{#SIMPLESTORAGE}].regexp(null)}=0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-disk-reader[{#FILENAME},Status.Health,{#SIMPLESTORAGE}].regexp(no batch file yet)}=0
trigger_prototype.name: Disk {#FILENAME} is not Healthy

discovery_rule.name: Thermal
discovery_rule.description: Find basic system traps to search into about Temperature on Chassis

trigger_prototype.expression: ({Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},ReadingCelsius,{#THERMAL}].last()} <= {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},LowerThresholdCritical,{#THERMAL}].last()})
trigger_prototype.name: Temperature Sensor {#FILENAME} is freezing at {ITEM.LASTVALUE}

trigger_prototype.expression: ({Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},ReadingCelsius,{#THERMAL}].last()} >= {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},UpperThresholdCritical,{#THERMAL}].last()})
trigger_prototype.name: Temperature Sensor {#FILENAME} is frying at {ITEM.LASTVALUE}

trigger_prototype.expression: ({Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},ReadingCelsius,{#THERMAL}].last()} <= {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},LowerThresholdNonCritical,{#THERMAL}].last()})
trigger_prototype.name: Temperature Sensor {#FILENAME} is pretty cold at {ITEM.LASTVALUE}

trigger_prototype.expression: ({Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},ReadingCelsius,{#THERMAL}].last()} >= {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},UpperThresholdNonCritical,{#THERMAL}].last()})
trigger_prototype.name: Temperature Sensor {#FILENAME} is pretty high at {ITEM.LASTVALUE}

trigger_prototype.expression: {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},Status.Health,{#THERMAL}].iregexp(OK)}=0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},Status.Health,{#THERMAL}].iregexp(null)}=0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{#FILENAME},Status.Health,{#THERMAL}].iregexp(no batch file yet)}=0
trigger_prototype.name: Temperature {#FILENAME} is not Healthy ({ITEM.LASTVALUE})

trigger.expression: ({Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{$IPMI}-System.Embedded.1.json,PowerState].iregexp(On)}=0) and ({Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{$IPMI}-System.Embedded.1.json,PowerState].iregexp(null)}=0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{$IPMI}-System.Embedded.1.json,PowerState].iregexp(no batch file yet)}=0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{$IPMI}-System.Embedded.1.json,PowerState].str(0)}=0)
trigger.name: {HOSNTAME} Indicating is powered off

trigger.expression: ({Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{$IPMI}-System.Embedded.1.json,MemorySummary.Status.Health].iregexp(OK)}=0) and ({Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{$IPMI}-System.Embedded.1.json,MemorySummary.Status.Health].iregexp(null)}=0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{$IPMI}-System.Embedded.1.json,MemorySummary.Status.Health].iregexp(no batch file yet)}=0)
trigger.name: {HOSNTAME} Memory Health is {ITEM.LASTVALUE}

trigger.expression: ({Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{$IPMI}-System.Embedded.1.json,Status.Health].iregexp(OK)}=0) and ({Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{$IPMI}-System.Embedded.1.json,Status.Health].iregexp(null)}=0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{$IPMI}-System.Embedded.1.json,Status.Health].iregexp(no batch file yet)}=0)
trigger.name: {HOSTNAME} Overall Server Status is {ITEM.LASTVALUE}

trigger.expression: ({Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{$IPMI}-System.Embedded.1.json,ProcessorSummary.Status.Health].iregexp(OK)}=0) and ({Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{$IPMI}-System.Embedded.1.json,ProcessorSummary.Status.Health].iregexp(null)}=0 and {Template Hw iDRAC Redfish LLD:redfish-reader[{$IPMI}-System.Embedded.1.json,ProcessorSummary.Status.Health].iregexp(no batch file yet)}=0)
trigger.name: {HOSTNAME} Processor Summary Health is {ITEM.LASTVALUE}
